OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FAs the war in Ukraine and Russia
OL,7,Fgrinds past its 1000th day, countries
OL,8,Fin Europe have begun releasing new
OL,9,Fsurvival guidance in the event of war.
OL,11,FTensions have inflamed across the past
OL,12,Ffew days, with Ukraine marking another
OL,13,Fmilestone in the conflict by firing
OL,14,Fsix long-range missiles, supplied by
OL,15,Fthe US, into Russian territory.
OL,17,FThe Kremlin says the strike could
OL,18,Fwarrant a nuclear response. On
OL,19,FWednesday the US announced it had
OL,20,Fclosed its embassy in Kyiv over fears
OL,21,Fof a "significant" air attack.
