OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FOn Monday, both Sweden and Finland
OL,7,Fupdated their guidance on how to
OL,8,Fsurvive in the event of war - but
OL,9,Fneither mention Russia by name.
OL,11,FThe two nations recently gave up
OL,12,Fneutrality and joined NATO in the wake
OL,13,Fof Russia's full-scale invasion of
OL,14,FUkraine.
OL,16,FSwedes were also told to "mentally
OL,17,Fprepare" for the possibility of war by
OL,18,Fthe country's former military
OL,19,Fcommander-in-chief, General Micael
OL,20,FByden, in January.
