OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FThe new guide will place a "greater
OL,7,Femphasis on preparing for war,"
OL,8,Faccording to a statement from the
OL,9,FSwedish Civil Contingencies Agency
OL,10,F(MSB) on Monday.
OL,12,FIt continued: "To resist these
OL,13,Fthreats, we must stand united and take
OL,14,Fresponsibility for our country. If we
OL,15,Fare attacked, everyone must help
OL,16,Fdefend Sweden's independence and our
OL,17,Fdemocracy. We build resilience every
OL,18,Fday ` together."
