OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FFinland has a land border with Russia
OL,7,Fof approximately 1,340 kilometers. The
OL,8,Fcountry's government, which compiled
OL,9,Fthe advice for citizens, stressed that
OL,10,F"preparedness is a civic skill in the
OL,11,Fcurrent global situation".
OL,13,FBoth Denmark and Norway have issued
OL,14,Fsimilar guides. In June, Danish
OL,15,Fauthorities released a PDF document
OL,16,Foutlining how citizens can prepare for
OL,17,F"crises".
