OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FIn June, Germany released an updated
OL,7,Foutline of its wartime plans,
OL,8,Fincluding conscription and rationing,
OL,9,Ffor the first time since the Cold War.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, German newspaper
OL,12,FFrankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung
OL,13,Freported the country's armed forces
OL,14,Fhad begun training companies on how to
OL,15,Frespond in the event of conflict.
OL,17,FWhat advice do they give?
