OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FSweden's updated guide was sent to
OL,7,Ffive million households, according to
OL,8,Fits government, and explains how
OL,9,Fcivilians should respond if the
OL,10,Fcountry comes under attack from
OL,11,Fnuclear, chemical or biological
OL,12,Fweapons.
OL,14,FIt said: "Take cover in the same way
OL,15,Fas with an airstrike. Shelters provide
OL,16,Fthe best protection. After a couple
OL,17,Fdays, the radiation has decreased
OL,18,Fsharply."
