OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FNew advice in the 2024 edition of
OL,7,FSweden's guide includes practical
OL,8,Ftips, including on evacuation and how
OL,9,Fto stop bleeding. It also gives tips
OL,10,Fon dealing with anxiety, how those
OL,11,Fwith pets should prepare, and how to
OL,12,Fspeak to children about crisis and war.
OL,14,FFresh guidance issued by Finland on
OL,15,FMonday advised citizens on power cuts,
OL,16,Fwater outages, communication
OL,17,Fblackouts, extreme weather and
OL,18,Fmilitary conflict.
