OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FThe new "German Operational Plan", as
OL,7,Freported by Frankfurter Allgemeine
OL,8,FZeitung, focused on the logistics of
OL,9,Fhow the country would respond if a
OL,10,FRussian attack led to Germany becoming
OL,11,Fa hub for hundreds of thousands of
OL,12,FNATO soldiers.
OL,14,FDenmark's guide from June advises
OL,15,Fhouseholds to make sure they have
OL,16,Fenough resources to survive for three
OL,17,Fdays in the event of a crisis,
OL,18,Fadvising on first aid, conserving
OL,19,Fwater and storing food.
OL,21,FWill the UK government do the same?
