OL,3,CWhich European countries are issuing
OL,4,Cfresh advice to survive war - and why?
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister's spokeswoman said
OL,7,Fthe UK is not currently considering
OL,8,Freleasing similar advice.
OL,10,FITV News' Deputy Political Editor
OL,11,FAnushka Asthana said it seems unlikely
OL,12,Fguidance will be issued imminently.
OL,14,F"One difference between us and Sweden,
OL,15,Fand Germany, is that they are a bit
OL,16,Fcloser to the border and a bit closer
OL,17,Fto where things could escalate," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,F"They feel that threat in more of a
OL,21,Freal way than we do."
